# Assets — whitelist approach
# Default: ignore everything under /assets/
# Track only what ships in production (project screenshots in V1).
# Moodboard refs are planning artifacts (referenced from .context/plans/) — do not commit (third-party screenshots, gets stale post-launch).
# /assets/private/ → personal files (CV, etc.)
# /assets/scratch/ → ad-hoc paste during sessions
# /assets/moodboard/ → design references; local-only
/assets/*
!/assets/projects/
!/assets/projects/**
